title: Computer Launcher
description:
Computer Launcher 

- Themes compatibility improved
- Menu blur issue fixed
- App duplication bug fixed in start menu + bug fixes
- Phone and Camera app launch issue fixed
- Wallpaper starching and live wallpaper issue fixed
- Help Screen loading fixed
- Performance improved
- Themes icon added on desktop
- Taskbar transparency improved
- Notification alerts can be disabled from settings
- Disable blur to see live wallpapers. (in settings)
- Windows 10 Like menu blur added
- Folder Icons changeable on desktop
